    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事背景</h2><br>这是一个奇幻而繁荣的世界，但某一天，可以通过梦境吞噬生命的黑暗力量突然出现，没有人能永远保持清醒，而睡着的人将被卷入梦境世界，被卷入之人只有通过战斗才能在这个充满危险的梦境中生存下来，胜者回归现实，败者魂归无期。<br><br>越来越多人陷落在梦境中无法回归现实，为了拯救世界，幻梦骑士团应运而生。这是由一群有能力抵抗暗黑力量侵蚀的人组成的团队。特殊的能力赋予了他们能够自由进入梦境的能力，于是他们一次又一次深入探索梦境世界的真相，寻找击败异世界的方法。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097620/extras/facc1bdec44c4bc45ed652631340e5ca.poster.avif?t=1700205458\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097620/extras/facc1bdec44c4bc45ed652631340e5ca.webm?t=1700205458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097620/extras/facc1bdec44c4bc45ed652631340e5ca.mp4?t=1700205458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><br>这是一款ACT+Roguelike游戏，游戏结合了经典街机游戏的玩法与风格，玩家一次次进入梦境世界战斗，游戏将兼有Roguelike游戏的高重玩性和街机游戏的爽快战斗体验。<br><br>每一次死亡并非毫无意义，你可以从梦境中带回一些物品，用以提升面板属性，或激活精灵技能，使自己更加强大。<br><br>每一次进入关卡都是不同的体验，因为梦境中的关卡和野怪都是随机出现的，通关隐藏关卡还能给你带来意外之喜。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097620/extras/355c7fcc5e30d0b62df74323aff617c2.poster.avif?t=1700205458\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097620/extras/355c7fcc5e30d0b62df74323aff617c2.webm?t=1700205458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097620/extras/355c7fcc5e30d0b62df74323aff617c2.mp4?t=1700205458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >四位英雄</h2><br>游戏中共有4名英雄可供选择，他们默认武器分别苗刀、弓箭、战斧，闪电鞭。武士主角还可以解锁3种新武器，让你在战斗中有更多选择。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097620/extras/1af0cafcf690a17197b87e53414270b7.poster.avif?t=1700205458\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097620/extras/1af0cafcf690a17197b87e53414270b7.webm?t=1700205458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097620/extras/1af0cafcf690a17197b87e53414270b7.mp4?t=1700205458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097620/extras/918bdd119b954ea91fe86fdec3bd5dfa.poster.avif?t=1700205458\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097620/extras/918bdd119b954ea91fe86fdec3bd5dfa.webm?t=1700205458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097620/extras/918bdd119b954ea91fe86fdec3bd5dfa.mp4?t=1700205458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
